<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, June 25 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index closed at
590.18 points Friday, up 0.05 percent from Thursday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 57,832 shares changed hands
in 284 deals, and the turnover was 915,279 dinars (83,207
U.S. dollars). 
</P>
