<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-26 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Panchen Lama Presided Successfully at Buddhist Ceremonies: Lamas (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XIGAZE, June 26 (Xinhua) -- The 11th Panchen Erdeni Qoigyijabu
has held successful Buddhist ceremonies in the Tibet Autonomous
Region, proving that the nine-year-old Panchen Lama is growing
healthily under the care of the central government.
</P>
<P>
"This is a forceful counterattack to the splittist attempts by
the Dalai Lama clique and hostile forces in the west, who use the
issue of the last Panchen Lama's reincarnation as a pretext," said
Lama Cering, director of the Democratic Management Committee of
Zhaxi Lhunbo Lamasery, the main residence of the Panchen Lama.
</P>
<P>
He made the remark in an exclusive interview with Xinhua.
</P>
<P>
The 11th Panchen Lama baptized lamas and disciples at the Zhaxi
Lhunbo Lamasery Thursday, reciting smoothly during the ceremony a
sutra on longevity more than 10,000 words long.
</P>
<P>
The Panchen Lama is regarded as the incarnation of the Buddha
of Longevity, and baptizing lamas and disciples to bring them
longevity is regarded as his special duty.
</P>
<P>
"The 11th Panchen Lama's successful baptism of his followers
convinced them that he is the true reincarnation of the 10th
Panchen Lama," said Lama Cering.
</P>
<P>
He added that the selection of the Panchen Lama through proper
religious rituals and historical tradition fulfills the wish of
lamas and believers in Tibetan Buddhism, and the lies and rumors
spread by the Dalai Lama's separatist clique as well as hostile
forces in the west are believed by nobody.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19990626.0064 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-26 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Panchen Lama Presides Successfully at Buddhist Ceremonies: Lamas (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The 11th Panchen Lama has been warmly received by lamas and
believers in both Lhasa, the capital of the Tibet Autonomous
Region, and Xigaze.
</P>
<P>
The Panchen's teachers voiced similar sentiments as those of
Lama Cering.
</P>
<P>
Widely respected for their great learning, noble character and
high prestige, the teachers expressed their amazement at the young
Panchen Lama's understanding of Buddhist tenets.
</P>
<P>
They also spoke highly of his compassion for all living beings
and his use of religious principles in daily life.
</P>
<P>
While spending most of his time studying Buddhism, the Panchen
Lama is also studying the Tibetan language, mathematics and
Chinese.
</P>
<P>
He has already learned a large number of sutras, and is able to
recite more than 60,000 words of them.
</P>
<P>
Keen on sports like jogging, cycling, football and ping pong,
the young Panchen Lama also shows a great interest in cameras.
</P>
<P>
Party and state leaders headed by President Jiang Zemin have
shown great concern for the healthy growth of the Panchen Lama,
who, in turn, has expressed his wish to follow the instructions of
President Jiang to become a good Living Buddha who loves the
country and the religion, and who contributes to social progress
and unity between the different ethnic groups in Tibet. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
