<HEADLINE> Spurs Beat Knicks to Win NBA Finals </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, June 25 (Xinhua) -- The San Antonio Spurs beat the
New York Knicks 78-77 to win the NBA Finals 4-1 here tonight.
</P>
